snippet: Third-ranked Andy Murray and No. 7 Juan Martín del Potro advanced at the BNP Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif.
abstract: Andy Murray defeats Evgeny Donskoy and Juan Martin del Potro defeats Nikolay Davydenko in the second round of the BNP Paribas Open tennis tournament.
lead_paragraph: Third-ranked Andy Murray and No. 7 Juan Martín del Potro advanced at the BNP Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif.
